      "x": 576,
      "y": 1052,
      "width": 328,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "roster/{name}/\n├── butler.toml\n│   identity, schedule, modules\n├── MANIFESTO.md\n│   public-facing identity\n├── CLAUDE.md\n│   butler personality / system prompt\n├── AGENTS.md\n│   runtime agent notes\n├── tools/\n│   butler-specific MCP tools\n├── api/\n│   ├── router.py  (exports 'router')\n│   └── models.py\n└── .agents/skills/\n    skills for runtime instances",
      "originalText": "roster/{name}/\n├── butler.toml\n│   identity, schedule, modules\n├── MANIFESTO.md\n│   public-facing identity\n├── CLAUDE.md\n│   butler personality / system prompt\n├── AGENTS.md\n│   runtime agent notes\n├── tools/\n│   butler-specific MCP tools\n├── api/\n│   ├── router.py  (exports 'router')\n│   └── models.py\n└── .agents/skills/\n    skills for runtime instances",
